text: Jaak Van Driessche (born 3 July 1969) is a Belgian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belgium Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Ghent
